<body>
{{> header (object user=user url=url) }}
<div class="about-container">
    <div>
        <h3 class="text-center">About</h3>
        <p>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <a href="https://github.com/Buggytheclown/hypeit"
                   class="href"
                   target="_blank"
                   rel="noopener">Open source</a> news aggregator (sources: Medium, Habr, DevTo).

            </li>
            <li><span class="about-info">Sorted by relative rating:
                    - Habr rating is `totalVotes`,
                    - Medium rating is `voterCount` // `!clapCount`
                    - Devto rating is `score/5` // `5` - magic number for the correct placement of posts among others
                </span>
            </li>
            <li>
                For registered users, we hide viewed messages and allow to make bookmarks.
            </li>

            <li>Medium posts can be proxed to remove any JS and cookies</li>

            <li>Show events (only dev.by currently), logged in user can manually hide the viewed events</li>
        </ul>


        For any suggestions or bug report you can contact: <a href="mailto: buggy.the.clown.md@gmail.com">buggy.the.clown.md@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
